### Register as a driver
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/drivers/register
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "licensePlate": "XYZ1234",
  "vehicleType": "car"
}

### Get driver by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/drivers/1

### Update availability status of the logged-in driver
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/drivers/me/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "availabilityStatus": "available"
}

### Update location of the logged-in driver
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/drivers/me/location
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 37.7749,
  "longitude": -122.4194
}

### Get all drivers (admin only)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/drivers
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Upload driver document
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/drivers/1/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="license.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./path/to/license.jpg
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="documentType"

driver_license
--boundary--
